Privacy Policy for Space Learners

Last Updated: October 28, 2024

1. Data Security

In Space Learners, we prioritize the security of your data. All information transmitted through the app is encrypted in transit to ensure its confidentiality and integrity.

2. Use of Data

We collect and use your data solely for the following purposes:

App Functionality: To provide you with personalized features and enhance the learning experience.
Account Management: To manage and secure your account, enabling full access to app functionalities.
Marketing: We may use some data to offer you promotions and updates about Space Learners.
3. Data Deletion

You have the right to request the deletion of your personal data at any time. To do so, please contact us at munon@munoncode.com, and we will process your request promptly.

Contact Us

For any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to reach out at munon@munoncode.com.
